12:06.050 --> 12:09.269
And your return won't be easy.

12:10.220 --> 12:11.050
No, I know.

12:13.270 --> 12:15.090
[chatter]

12:17.610 --> 12:18.429
Hey.

12:20.190 --> 12:22.351
Hi! Hi. [giggles]

12:22.610 --> 12:23.440
Hey.

12:24.070 --> 12:25.310
-You're back!
-I am.

12:25.410 --> 12:27.731
-Wow. You look good.
-Thanks.

12:27.830 --> 12:30.401
Yeah, apparently, natural sunlight
and physical exercise

12:30.490 --> 12:32.151
are, like, good for us or something.

12:32.250 --> 12:33.740
-Something. [chuckles]
-Something.

12:33.830 --> 12:36.492
The good news is that I'm back in time
for the Spring Fling.

12:36.750 --> 12:40.083
And I was determined
to make it back in time to take you.

12:40.670 --> 12:43.002
-Oh.
-I mean, or we could just blow it off.

12:43.090 --> 12:45.422
-We could do something else.
-Yeah, no, I mean...

12:46.300 --> 12:49.884
