15:44.980 --> 15:46.186
[car horn honking]

15:48.610 --> 15:50.601
["Lovely" playing]

15:51.070 --> 15:52.981
[Clay] Memories are sometimes a relief.

16:02.160 --> 16:03.661
And sometimes they're torture.

16:04.000 --> 16:04.955
[Hannah] I was right.

16:05.580 --> 16:07.491
You're the most courageous nerd
