17:40.350 --> 17:41.169
Then don't.

17:43.770 --> 17:46.978
The thing I'm second most afraid of
is I'll never be able to let you go.

17:50.360 --> 17:51.896
Do you remember the winter dance?

17:53.230 --> 17:54.390
