to think of that right now.

18:16.050 --> 18:20.168
Heart made of glass
My mind of stone

18:20.260 --> 18:24.299
- Tear me to pieces, skin to bone
- Tear me to pieces, skin to bone

18:24.890 --> 18:29.099
