32:13.970 --> 32:16.928
I knew those kids could
fuck everything up for us, and they did.

32:17.470 --> 32:18.846
Well, you helped.

32:21.480 --> 32:25.018
I... Tell me what you want me to do.

32:25.610 --> 32:28.317
-Okay? I'll make it right.
-I want you to leave it alone.

32:30.190 --> 32:31.430
