33:02.230 --> 33:05.131
Those fucking jocks were not happy
about the field and the season.

33:07.360 --> 33:09.430
-Yeah. I'll be careful.
-Good.

33:09.610 --> 33:10.429
And you know...

33:12.400 --> 33:13.230
about everything...

33:13.610 --> 33:16.101
Yeah. No, me, too. Yeah.

33:16.610 --> 33:19.192
-It got a little fucked up.
-[chuckles] Yeah, totally.

33:20.490 --> 33:21.320
Hey.

33:22.410 --> 33:26.289
You know, being away,
it was really good.

33:27.250 --> 33:29.832
And I realized a lot of shit, so...

33:30.090 --> 33:31.660
-You know.
-That's good, man.

33:31.750 --> 33:34.378
-[chuckles]
-So, we're all right?

33:34.800 --> 33:35.789
Yeah, for sure.

33:35.880 --> 33:37.336
-Cool. [chuckles]
-Yeah.

33:37.760 --> 33:40.001
