34:00.870 --> 34:04.158
It's insane,
but it's, like, not a surprise, I guess.

34:04.620 --> 34:07.032
And I-I just feel this peace
that it's over.

34:07.120 --> 34:07.950
So, it's over?

34:08.330 --> 34:10.412
No trial, no more legal stuff?
Done?

34:10.790 --> 34:11.620
Done.

34:13.170 --> 34:14.000
And I'm good.

34:14.880 --> 34:19.214
Oh, what a fine parade

34:20.090 --> 34:24.800
Ready or not, call your name

34:25.180 --> 34:27.842
Hey, now, where do I go?

34:28.640 --> 34:30.301
[Justin sighs]

34:31.860 --> 34:33.179
You gonna go to this dance?

34:35.990 --> 34:37.730
What, the Spring Fling thing?

34:38.860 --> 34:41.408
-Why in the world would I go to that?
-I don't know.

34:41.870 --> 34:43.076
It... It might be fun?

34:43.790 --> 34:44.984
I don't go to dances.

34:46.370 --> 34:47.200
You can go.

34:47.620 --> 34:48.530
No.

34:49.830 --> 34:53.334
I just thought
that it'd be my first thing back

34:53.420 --> 34:59.177
and I could show people
that I'm not, like, hiding or whatever.

35:02.930 --> 35:04.420
[clicks tongue] Forget it.

35:07.560 --> 35:08.379
Fuck.

35:09.390 --> 35:11.802
Fine. [scoffs] We'll go.

35:13.690 --> 35:14.645
[chuckles]

35:15.070 --> 35:19.359
I just thought since I hadn't heard
from you after I told you about Lucas--

35:19.450 --> 35:20.906
