like you really wanted me to call back.

35:25.080 --> 35:27.196
Okay, okay. Seriously?

35:27.950 --> 35:29.827
I think you're used to people chasing you.

35:30.710 --> 35:32.621
And you're used to getting away.

35:35.420 --> 35:36.239
Maybe.

35:36.960 --> 35:39.588
Well, you're not getting away.

35:48.810 --> 35:49.799
I should be on my way.

35:52.480 --> 35:53.549
Thank you for coming.

35:53.650 --> 35:57.973
Thank you for... for having us.

35:58.820 --> 36:00.811
I saw the store's for lease.

36:01.900 --> 36:03.151
I'm moving to New York.

36:04.320 --> 36:05.617
It was always Hannah's dream.

36:05.700 --> 36:09.079
She never made it,
so I'll get there for her.

36:10.960 --> 36:11.779
I...

36:14.920 --> 36:18.242
I wasn't sure
if I should share this with you,

36:18.340 --> 36:20.410
but after hearing
what you said, I think...

36:22.090 --> 36:23.170
I think it's all right.

36:31.430 --> 36:35.434
I found it on one of the old computers
when I was cleaning up the store.

36:39.110 --> 36:40.020
Hannah wrote it.

36:53.830 --> 36:54.956
"Reasons why not."

36:56.080 --> 36:57.069
You're on there.

36:57.540 --> 37:00.919
At least once, possibly twice.

37:01.010 --> 37:03.831
Did... did she call you "Helmet"?

37:06.720 --> 37:08.347
[chuckles] Yeah, she did.

37:13.430 --> 37:14.590
Eleven reasons.

37:15.560 --> 37:18.051
She came up just short.

37:19.230 --> 37:21.471
But she left so many out.
You know that, don't you?

37:21.780 --> 37:26.524
No matter how many reasons
there might be "why,"

37:27.370 --> 37:28.814
there are always more "why not."

37:30.490 --> 37:31.320
I do.

37:40.750 --> 37:42.957
I wish I knew you when she was alive.

37:48.550 --> 37:50.040
I wish you'd known me then, too.

37:53.100 --> 37:53.919
Well...

37:56.100 --> 37:56.930
bye.

37:58.810 --> 37:59.640
Bye.

38:13.540 --> 38:14.495
[door opens]

38:17.710 --> 38:19.780
