38:34.470 --> 38:37.268
-If I hurt you in any way--
-They canceled our fucking season.

38:39.020 --> 38:41.477
I was acting out of a lot of anger
and confusion.

38:41.560 --> 38:43.266
-Oh, yeah?
-And I'm going to do better.

38:43.730 --> 38:45.982
And I hope that we can learn
to talk to each other--

38:46.280 --> 38:48.441
[grunting]

38:49.070 --> 38:51.948
God! You ruined
my fucking life, faggot!

38:53.030 --> 38:53.860
Get up!

38:54.450 --> 38:56.691
-[water bubbling]
-[groaning]

38:57.290 --> 38:59.576
[gasps] I'm sorry!
Please, I'm sorry!

39:01.210 --> 39:02.029
Hold him!

39:03.540 --> 39:05.337
[gasping] I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

39:09.260 --> 39:11.046
[groans]

39:11.680 --> 39:13.386
