39:47.210 --> 39:48.256
We can do better.

39:49.590 --> 39:52.969
_ But we still live in a world_
that is out to break us any way it can.

39:54.850 --> 39:57.216
-Yo, so how's the car?
-It's getting pretty close.

39:57.600 --> 39:59.670
I've been working on it
every hour I'm not in school

39:59.770 --> 40:01.260
and some when I should be in school.

40:01.350 --> 40:04.433
